These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-8-1::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: metal, country, rock
1. the fan of metal is on the far right##1
2. the fan of metal is not to the left of the fan of country##8
3. the fan of rock is somewhere to the left of the fan of country##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |    2    |    3     |
| Music-Genre   | rock | country | metal |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-8-2::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: blues, dubstep, soul
1. the fan of soul is not to the left of the fan of blues##8
2. the fan of soul is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1   |   2    |     3     |
| Music-Genre   | blues | soul | dubstep |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-8-3::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: quad-bike, airplane, tram
1. the person driving the airplane is on the left of the person driving the quad-bike##1
2. the person driving the quad-bike is not to the right of the person driving the tram##8

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2   |  3  |
| Transport   | airplane | quad-bike | tram |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-8-4::.
