1. the person who's sport is rowing is not to the left of the person who's sport is skiing##8
2. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the right of the person who's sport is rowing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |  2   |      3      |
| Sport   | skiing | rowing | snowboarding |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-8-5::.
City: marseilles, liverpool, prague
1. the person traveling to liverpool is in an even position##4
2. the person traveling to liverpool is not to the right of the person traveling to prague##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |     3     |
| City   | marseilles | liverpool | prague |

